impacts.Description: Number of head-to ball impacts from observation by research study team members

Dpre.LongName: dprime on the DPX task before the season
Dpre.Description: A unitless measure of response accuracy calculated by subtracting BX false alarm rate from the accuracy rate on AX trials

Dpost.LongName: dprime on the DPX task after the season
Dpost.Description: A unitless measure of response accuracy calculated by subtracting BX false alarm rate from the accuracy rate on AX trials

PBIpre.LongName: proactive behavior index on the DPX task before the season
PBIpre.Description: A measure of accuracy (%) reprsenting a balance of interference between AY and BX trials; +PBI ~ proactive control / -PBI ~ reactive control.

PBIpost.LongName: proactive behavior index on the DPX task after the season
PBIpost.Description: A measure of accuracy (%) reprsenting a balance of interference between AY and BX trials; +PBI ~ proactive control / -PBI ~ reactive control.

README: Resting-state fMRI collected pre- and post-season on collegiate Men's Soccer, Men's Cross-Country, and Men's Golf athletes.
